description.en:
What is the project about?
$SHROOM is an AI "choose your own adventure" memecoin, where daily green or red trading wicks shape the direction of an AI-generated storyline. The world’s first ever AI memecoin that is building a community through interactive story telling. 

What makes your project unique?
- First anime memecoin
- First AI memecoin that is building a community through interactive story telling
- ChatGPT x MidJourney AI led memecoin
- First ‘Choose-your-own-adventure’ concept in web3

History of your project.
With $SHROOMS, you're joining a community of adventurers and explorers who use their trading decisions to shape the direction of an AI generated story. We started as a team of anime lovers looking to build the next great memecoin

What’s next for your project?
- CEX lisitings
- Community activities
- Storyline updates

What can your token be used for?
- SHROOMS is a memecoin

What is the project about?
$SHROOM is an AI "choose your own adventure" memecoin, where daily green or red trading wicks shape the direction of an AI-generated storyline. The world’s first ever AI memecoin that is building a community through interactive story telling. 

What makes your project unique?
- First anime memecoin
- First AI memecoin that is building a community through interactive story telling
